(1) East River Drive, north from East 92nd Street. This section being a new thoroughfare, following the river's edge northward to East 107th Street; where Pleasant Ave., is incorporated. Note portion of the Astoria Ferry House on the right. August 3, 1936.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) A later view, north from about 93rd Street. March 29, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.

(3) A view mainly of the east side and showing the curve at 96th Street. March 29, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.
